    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "郊外での合宿所で行われる夏合宿。\r\n様々なウマ娘たちが己の課題に取り組む中――",
            "enText": "We were here at the city's outskirts where the summer training \ncamp took place, and among the multitude of horsegirls hard \nat work on their own regimens there was ——",
            "nextBlock": 2,
