                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4375708071657364148,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "TM Opera O",
            "jpText": "はぁ……はぁ……トレーナー君。\r\nどうだったかな、ボクの華麗なステップは？",
            "enText": "<i>Haa… haa…</i> My dear trainer, how are you \nfinding my graceful steps?",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 211,
            "voiceIdx": 2,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "凄い勢いだったな",
                    "enText": "Very energetic indeed.",
                    "nextBlock": 8
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "凄い勢いだったね",
                    "enText": "Very energetic indeed.",
                    "nextBlock": 8
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 66,
                    "pathId": -8662934849266944539
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 8406142607109562774
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 18,
                    "pathId": 7352960868929889389
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 18,
                    "pathId": -7740330768096633880
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6405265373450178818,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "TM Opera O",
            "jpText": "はーっはっはっは！　いい視点だよ、トレーナー君。\r\n今回のテーマは『内なる自分の解放』だからね。",
            "enText": "<i>Haa-ha-ha-ha!</i> An astute observation, my dear trainer. \nFor today's theme is no other than \"releasing my inner self\".",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 324,
            "voiceIdx": 3,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 105,
                    "pathId": -9077557697250562456
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 10,
                    "pathId": -8171985768477914602
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6667759154957115551,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "TM Opera O",
            "jpText": "海で鍛えられるのは筋力だけじゃない。\r\n己を表現し、自己を解き放つことで得られる強さもあるのさ。",
            "enText": "The beach offers training opportunities beyond simple \nphysical strength. A certain strength can be attained \nthrough expressing oneself, freeing one's inner being.",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "origClipLength": 277,
            "voiceIdx": 4,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 256,
                    "pathId": 4671260766143996548
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -5578334401446772096
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 452672957298421740,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "TM Opera O",
            "jpText": "時に優雅に、時に激しく水面を震わせる。\r\nマーメイドすら嫉妬する、水辺の滑走を見ていたまえ！",
            "enText": "One's wake at times elegant, and at times tempestuous. \nObserve as yours truly glides over the water's edge with \nthe grace to turn mermaid's heads in envy!",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "origClipLength": 337,
            "voiceIdx": 5,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 58,
                    "pathId": 4072304146649917554
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 1632334119605907499
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7020675565154603387,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "中堅トレーナーA",
            "enName": "Experienced Trainer A",
            "jpText": "ウワサには聞いていたけど……彼女、その……すごいわね。\r\n海ではしゃぐ気持ちはわかるけど……。",
            "enText": "I've heard of her antics but… seeing her in person is… \nreally something. Not that I don't understand the desire \nto play around at the beach……",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "origClipLength": 297,
            "voiceIdx": 6,
            "pathId": -3747842273993260866,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ウマ娘A",
            "enName": "Horsegirl A",
            "jpText": "あ、あはは……なんかこう、“オペラオーさん”って感じですよね。\r\nレースの時もいつも余裕っていうか……。",
            "enText": "A-Ahaha…… It's very Opera O-esque behavior. \nEven when racing she has that air of freedom…",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "origClipLength": 299,
            "voiceIdx": 7,
            "pathId": 4516217638520824582,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "という声も、ちらほら聞こえては来るが――",
            "enText": "I could overhear such comments occasionally… however ——",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "origClipLength": 71,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 66,
                    "pathId": 6194651197168361531
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2865306419056078870,
            "blockIdx": 13
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "TM Opera O",
            "jpText": "さあ、ここでターンだ！\r\n脚で砂をかき上げ、蝶が羽ばたくように飛びたつっ！",
            "enText": "This calls for a turn! Sweep up the sand with my foot and \nleap upward like a butterfly taking flight!",
            "nextBlock": 15,
            "origClipLength": 220,
            "voiceIdx": 8,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 4601514768148949287
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -8055807945147542946
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 3799047311477088838
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6848056729011710353,
            "blockIdx": 14
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "TM Opera O",
            "jpText": "白い雲、青い海、潮騒に交じる美しいボク！\r\nこの夏は1度しかない！　ならば全力を出し切るまでさっ！",
            "enText": "White clouds, blue seas, and my handsome self weaving \nbetween the crashing sound of the waves! We can only enjoy \nthis summer once! Hence we should use every moment!",
            "nextBlock": 16,
            "origClipLength": 361,
            "voiceIdx": 9,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 60,
                    "pathId": 2098017917988943286
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 65,
                    "pathId": 2046850249871435905
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 28,
                    "pathId": 2675126620352234629
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 28,
                    "pathId": 4978018183991220878
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4174474469610719398,
            "blockIdx": 15
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "……どのような行動であれ、\r\nテイエムオペラオーは本気で取り組んでいる。",
            "enText": "—— No matter what she takes on, TM Opera O \nalways faces it earnestly, with all she has.",
            "nextBlock": 17,
            "origClipLength": 91,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 50,
                    "pathId": 4578351736769786347
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 110,
                    "pathId": 6678329040108216944
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5980364223595171475,
            "blockIdx": 16
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "確固たる意志で努力し、目標に突き進む担当ウマ娘がいるならば、\r\nその背を押すのがトレーナーの役目だろう。",
            "enText": "Needless to say, when a horsegirl exhibits such resolute will, \nto diligently press on until her goals are met, it is her trainer's \nduty to support her every step of the way.",
            "nextBlock": 18,
            "origClipLength": 112,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "一緒に最高のトレーニングにしよう！",
                    "enText": "Let's go get some stellar training in!",
                    "nextBlock": 18
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 139,
                    "pathId": -1223909380464988948
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -6208879800001500655
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4377030087601463756,
            "blockIdx": 17
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "TM Opera O",
            "jpText": "勿論だ！　手は一切抜かないとも！！\r\n大海原とボクのハーモニーを、このビーチ中に響かせよう！",
            "enText": "But of course! We won't settle for half measures!! \nThe harmonious melody of yours truly and the deep \nblue will ring out over this very beach!",
            "nextBlock": 19,
            "origClipLength": 306,
            "voiceIdx": 10,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 66,
                    "pathId": -2667217944510649208
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 63,
                    "pathId": 1487295424924166144
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1124155704390304686,
            "blockIdx": 18
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "その日のトレーニング終了後――",
            "enText": "After training that day ——",
            "nextBlock": 20,
            "origClipLength": 64,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 26,
                    "pathId": 4892160536412210098
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 31,
                    "pathId": -7861288602612571806
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6049796017985467246,
            "blockIdx": 19
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "TM Opera O",
            "jpText": "ここにいたんだね、トレーナー君。",
            "enText": "Oh there you are, my dear trainer.",
            "nextBlock": 21,
            "origClipLength": 79,
            "voiceIdx": 11,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "どうしたんだ？",
                    "enText": "Is something wrong?",
                    "nextBlock": 21
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "どうしたの？",
                    "enText": "Is something wrong?",
                    "nextBlock": 21
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 33,
                    "pathId": -900661483451733878
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 92,
                    "pathId": 4503665460909942456
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 50,
                    "pathId": -2067308348084149613
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 50,
                    "pathId": -86608702749225154
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -325906735392562304,
            "blockIdx": 20
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "TM Opera O",
            "jpText": "なに、いくつか相談したいことがあってね。",
            "enText": "Oh nothing, I simply want to request advice on a few topics.",
            "nextBlock": 22,
            "origClipLength": 114,
            "voiceIdx": 12,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 50,
                    "pathId": 8747889076955046894
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 30,
                    "pathId": -8466239595321469542
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 22,
                    "pathId": -5726392213217420997
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 22,
                    "pathId": 5037097890905587392
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6897938954058918198,
            "blockIdx": 21
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "TM Opera O",
            "jpText": "まずは明日のメニューの確認だが、\r\n集合時間は4時にして――",
            "enText": "First of all, regarding tomorrow's regimen… \nWe can meet up at 4 in the morning ——",
            "nextBlock": 23,
            "origClipLength": 165,
            "voiceIdx": 13,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "早い早い！",
                    "enText": "That's way too early!",
                    "nextBlock": 23
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 63,
                    "pathId": 8388582936262351029
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 1009480580859650982
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2545275657016084864,
            "blockIdx": 22
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "TM Opera O",
            "jpText": "そうかな？　……ああ、なるほど！\r\n夏とはいえど、まだ朝日も昇る途中だ。",
            "enText": "You think so? …Ah, I see! Even in summer \nthe morning sun would still be rising.",
            "nextBlock": 24,
            "origClipLength": 230,
            "voiceIdx": 14,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 154,
                    "pathId": -4154309686358620147
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 3387498159676144716
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1546733554866202879,
            "blockIdx": 23
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "TM Opera O",
            "jpText": "太陽を背にさっそうと現れるボクの演出をするならば、\r\nもう少し後の時間の方が適しているね、了解だよ。",
            "enText": "It would be best to choose a slightly later time if yours truly \nis to appear silhouetted against the sun! Very well.",
            "nextBlock": 25,
            "origClipLength": 280,
            "voiceIdx": 15,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 50,
                    "pathId": 3604051776476266464
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 113,
                    "pathId": 9220672079826550889
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7681014265878005541,
            "blockIdx": 24
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "TM Opera O",
            "jpText": "ふむ……それで集合した後は、\r\nボクは髪をかき上げながら、ゆっくりと海の中に入る。",
            "enText": "Hmm… after meeting up then, yours truly will gently enter \nthe sea while running a hand through her hair.",
            "nextBlock": 26,
            "origClipLength": 251,
            "voiceIdx": 16,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 164,
                    "pathId": 6800992100852020846
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 107,
                    "pathId": -3648210105113922433
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8146648238271558806,
            "blockIdx": 25
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "TM Opera O",
            "jpText": "イソギンチャクと触れ合う魚のように、\r\n波に揺れ、美しく舞い、シンクロを開始して――",
            "enText": "Floating through the waters like a fish among anemones, \na beautiful synchronized dance ——",
            "nextBlock": 27,
            "origClipLength": 223,
            "voiceIdx": 17,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "毒があるイソギンチャクには気を付けような",
                    "enText": "Careful, those things can be poisonous.",
                    "nextBlock": 27
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "毒があるイソギンチャクには気を付けようね",
                    "enText": "Careful, those things can be poisonous.",
                    "nextBlock": 27
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 99,
                    "pathId": -5527648300277874592
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 74,
                    "pathId": -3129379160612843410
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3418395201623344449,
            "blockIdx": 26
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "TM Opera O",
            "jpText": "おや、そうなのかい。ではこの白魚のような手足が\r\nイソギンチャクに触れないよう十分に注意しよう。",
            "enText": "Oh, is that so? Then yours truly will take great care \nso as to not let her limbs, pale and slender as icefish, \ncome into contact with the anemones.",
            "nextBlock": 28,
            "origClipLength": 286,
            "voiceIdx": 18,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 220,
                    "pathId": 8151849787152007021
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 30,
                    "pathId": 4565624406179591447
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4992756015640013486,
            "blockIdx": 27
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "TM Opera O",
            "jpText": "そしてしばらくしてボクは海から上がり、水しぶきと共に歌いだす！\r\n真夏のセイレーンたちも惚れ込んでしまう歌声でね！",
            "enText": "And after rising from the seas again, she shall join the splashing \nof the waves in song! With a voice to charm midsummer's sirens!",
            "nextBlock": 29,
            "origClipLength": 333,
            "voiceIdx": 19,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "歌も歌うのか！？",
                    "enText": "You intend on singing too!?",
                    "nextBlock": 29
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "歌も歌うの！？",
                    "enText": "You intend on singing too!?",
                    "nextBlock": 29
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 50,
                    "pathId": 3466905702258923167
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 50,
                    "pathId": -2712341470355500125
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7208867923404789541,
            "blockIdx": 28
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "TM Opera O",
            "jpText": "レース後のライブと同じさ。\r\nフィニッシュを飾るなら、人の心を揺さぶる歌でないと。",
            "enText": "It's no different from an after-race performance. One seeks \nthe uplifting melody of song to effect a graceful end.",
            "nextBlock": 30,
            "origClipLength": 211,
            "voiceIdx": 20,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 22,
                    "pathId": -1943228720585172983
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 5776626587420968065
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4809619145855419789,
            "blockIdx": 29
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "TM Opera O",
            "jpText": "ビーチにいる人々は感涙し、万雷の拍手をボクに送るだろう。\r\n嗚呼、完っ璧だ……！",
            "enText": "My dear beachgoing audience will be moved to tears, and surely \nsend a thunderous applause my way. Ah, true perfection…!",
            "nextBlock": 31,
            "origClipLength": 292,
            "voiceIdx": 21,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 57,
                    "pathId": 7183380858630505060
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 87,
                    "pathId": 4455802926797503885
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7086872864401834320,
            "blockIdx": 30
